      "text": "总企划 : 郑翰文/沈炳@Flowsixteen",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 19.8,
      "time_str": "00:19.800",
      "text": "I love u",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 22.35,
      "time_str": "00:22.350",
      "text": "这句话我经常对你讲",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 24.24,
      "time_str": "00:24.240",
      "text": "你是我想含在嘴里的一块糖",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.91,
      "time_str": "00:26.910",
      "text": "铁石心肠最后敌不过你的倔强",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 29.55,
      "time_str": "00:29.550",
      "text": "像个孩子总想钻进你的胸膛",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 32.25,
      "time_str": "00:32.250",
      "text": "很多次走在凌晨三点半的大街",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.89,
      "time_str": "00:34.890",
      "text": "也曾为了找到紫霞仙子踏破铁鞋",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.44,
      "time_str": "00:37.440",
      "text": "Obb obb我发誓我会努力",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.14,
      "time_str": "00:40.140",
      "text": "Obb obb我发誓我会走起",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.75,
      "time_str": "00:42.750",
      "text": "我希望你能陪我走过白天和黑夜",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 45.48,
      "time_str": "00:45.480",
      "text": "也希望能抱着你回味美梦一整夜",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.09,
      "time_str": "00:48.090",
      "text": "你懂我想要的每一个体会",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 51.0,
      "time_str": "00:51.000",
      "text": "今晚陪我大家都别想入睡",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 53.46,
      "time_str": "00:53.460",
      "text": "我想要看你身上洁白婚纱的模样",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 56.22,
      "time_str": "00:56.220",
      "text": "在你脑海里留下属于我的记号",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 58.77,
      "time_str": "00:58.770",
      "text": "我想要看你在我心上自由飞翔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 61.62,
      "time_str": "01:01.620",
      "text": "从大到小的过程记录在你的大脑",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.17,
      "time_str": "01:04.170",
      "text": "我带你走过春夏秋冬不想太普通",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 66.93,
      "time_str": "01:06.930",
      "text": "你知道我想爱你所以是我主动",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 69.3,
      "time_str": "01:09.300",
      "text": "我见到你第一眼",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 70.68,
      "time_str": "01:10.680",
      "text": "就知道你是我的菜",
      "translation": null
    },
